All Implemented Interfaces:
MultiMap<K,V>, MustInitializeOrLoad
public class BTree<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements MultiMap<K,V>, MustInitializeOrLoad

The Btree page, all leafs and innernodes have to be stored in the same RawPageManager. We used to have it differently but it is simpler this way. Now The BTree can make sure that all use the same serializers and comparators.

Header: NUM_OF_ENTRIES ROOT_ID (here comes serializers etc)
